  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Contribution to IOCC/Apostoli ACT Appeal for Greece</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Providing immediate emergency shelter and protection to refugees.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to IOCC (International Orthodox Christian Charities) in Greece through the ACT Alliance appeal, enabling the partner to support UNHCR, Police and the local municipal authorities to convert a disused factory building on the island of Chios into a migrant/refugee reception center that can accommodate up to 1,000 persons with all appropriate services and protection.</narrative>
  </description>
